\item Find $v_{C_0}(0-), v_{C_0}(0+)$ and  $v_{C_0}(\infty) $. 

\solution From the initial conditions,
\begin{align}
    v_{C_0}(0-) = \frac{q_1}{C} = \SI[parse-numbers=false]{\frac{4}{3}}{\V}
